## Third-Party Licenses

This project uses open-source software. Below are the licenses for key dependencies:

### MIT Licensed Packages

- **@elevenlabs/react** - ElevenLabs React SDK
- **@react-three/drei** - React Three Fiber helpers
- **@react-three/fiber** - React renderer for Three.js
- **three** - 3D graphics library
- **socket.io** / **socket.io-client** - Real-time bidirectional communication
- **next** - React framework
- **react** / **react-dom** - React library
- **hono** - Fast web framework
- **axios** - HTTP client
- **tailwind-merge** - Utility for merging Tailwind classes
- **clsx** - Utility for constructing className strings
- **shadcn** - UI component library
- **@base-ui/react** - Unstyled UI components
- **tw-animate-css** - Tailwind CSS animations

### BSD-2-Clause Licensed Packages

- **chess.js** - Chess move generation/validation library
